that would otherwise infringe the licensor's copyright in
it for any permitted purpose. However, you may
only distribute the software according to [Distribution
License](#distribution-license--分发许可) and make changes or new works
based on the software according to [Changes and New Works
License](#changes-and-new-works-license--变更与衍生作品许可).

许可方授予您一项版权许可，允许您在许可目的范围内对软件执行任何
可能侵犯许可方版权的操作。但是，您只能根据[分发许可](#distribution-license--分发许可)
分发软件，并根据[变更与衍生作品许可](#changes-and-new-works-license--变更与衍生作品许可)
对软件进行修改或创作衍生作品。

## Distribution License | 分发许可

The licensor grants you an additional copyright license
to distribute copies of the software. Your license
to distribute covers distributing the software with
changes and new works permitted by [Changes and New Works
License](#changes-and-new-works-license--变更与衍生作品许可).

许可方授予您额外的版权许可，允许您分发软件副本。您的分发许可
涵盖分发经[变更与衍生作品许可](#changes-and-new-works-license--变更与衍生作品许可)
