any other licenses.

本条款不允许您将您的任何许可再许可或转让给他人，也不阻止许可方
向他人授予许可。本条款不暗示任何其他许可。

## Patent Defense | 专利抗辩

If you make any written claim that the software infringes or
contributes to infringement of any patent, your licenses for
the software granted under these terms end immediately. If your
company makes such a claim, your licenses end immediately for
work on behalf of your company.

如果您以书面形式声称本软件侵犯或促成侵犯任何专利，您在本条款下
获得的软件许可将立即终止。如果您的公司提出此类声称，您代表公司
所进行工作的许可将立即终止。

## Violations | 违规

The first time you are notified in writing that you have
violated any of these terms, or terms of any other licenses
provided with the software, your licenses granted under these
terms can be restored. To do so, you must cure the violation
within thirty days of receiving notice. Otherwise, your
licenses end immediately.

首次书面通知您违反本条款或随软件提供的任何其他许可条款时，您在
本条款下获得的许可可以恢复。为此，您必须在收到通知后三十天内
纠正违规行为。否则，您的许可将立即终止。

## No Liability | 免责声明

***As far as the law allows, the software comes as is, without any
warranty or condition, and the licensor will not be liable to
you for any damages arising out of these terms or the use or
nature of the software, under any kind of legal claim.***

***在法律允许的最大范围内，本软件按"原样"提供，不附带任何保证或
条件，许可方不对因本条款或软件的使用或性质而产生的任何损害承担
责任，无论基于何种法律主张。***

## Definitions | 定义

The **licensor** is the individual or entity offering these
terms, and the **software** is the software the licensor makes
available under these terms.

**许可方**是提供本条款的个人或实体，**软件**是许可方在本条款下
提供的软件。

**You** refers to the individual or entity agreeing to these
terms.

**您**指同意本条款的个人或实体。

**Your company** is any legal entity, sole proprietorship,
or other kind of organization that you work for, plus all
organizations that have control over, are under the control
of, or are under common control with that organization.
**Control** means ownership of substantially all the assets of
an entity, or the power to direct its management and policies
by vote, contract, or otherwise. Control can be direct or
indirect.

**您的公司**是指您工作的任何法人实体、个人独资企业或其他类型的
组织，以及对该组织拥有控制权、受该组织控制或与该组织处于共同
控制下的所有组织。**控制**是指拥有实体几乎全部资产的所有权，或
通过表决、合同或其他方式指导其管理和政策的权力。控制可以是直接
的或间接的。

**Your licenses** are all the licenses granted to you for the
software under these terms.

**您的许可**是指在本条款下授予您的所有软件许可。

**Use** means anything you do with the software requiring one
of your licenses.

**使用**是指您对软件所做的任何需要您的许可之一的事情。
